headline.print_headline: Karlovic Stops Against No. 19 Anderson at French
headline.main: Karlovic Stops Against No. 19 Anderson at French

lead_paragraph: Ivo Karlovic of Croatia stopped playing because of an injury after losing the first set of his third-round French Open match Saturday against 19th-seeded Kevin Anderson of South Africa.
